{"id":166951,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/global-voices-马来西亚：净选盟游行網絡记录/","date":"2011-07-12T23:00:23Z","modified":"2011-07-12T23:00:23Z","title":"Global Voices | 马来西亚：净选盟游行網絡记录","content":"<p><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://bersih.org/\" href=\"http://bersih.org/\">净选盟2.0</a>（Bersih 2.0）于7月9日发动游行，要求马来西亚落实选举改革，结果超过1400人遭到逮捕，警方使用催泪瓦斯驱赶群众，主办单位宣称现场共有五万人，“Bersih”在马来文意指“干净”。</p>\n<p>马国政府先前将净选盟列为<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/01/malaysia-planned-rally-calling-for-fair-elections-banned/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/01/malaysia-planned-rally-calling-for-fair-elections-banned/\">非法组织</a>，后来又批准在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/07/malaysia-online-reactions-to-bersih-2-0-rally/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/07/malaysia-online-reactions-to-bersih-2-0-rally/\">体育馆</a>里举行活动，但场馆管理单位又拒绝发出活动许可。净选盟原本计划要提交<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://bersih.org/?page_id=4111\" href=\"http://bersih.org/?page_id=4111\">八项诉求</a>给政府。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2195653096710&#038;set=o.213938935311531&#038;type=1\"><img title=\"Bersih rally from the Facebook page of Yuvanesh Prabakaran \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/bersih-rally-375x225.jpg\" alt=\"Bersih rally from the Facebook page of Yuvanesh Prabakaran \" width=\"375\" height=\"225\" /></a></p>\n<p>净选盟游行照片，来自Facebook页面Yuvanesh Prabakaran </p>\n</div>\n<p>净选盟<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://bersih.org/?p=4397\" href=\"http://bersih.org/?p=4397\">指导委员会</a>于7月9日晚间发表声明：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>净选盟2.0备感骄傲，尽管被迫面对重重阻碍，马来西亚各界民众仍克服警方迫害，大批和平走上街头，展现对国家与司法原则的爱。</p>\n<p>但我们对数百人遭到逮捕相当震惊，其中许多案例根本毫无来由。</p>\n<p>这场游行不是终点，而是马来西亚清廉公平选举漫漫长路的其中一步，我们会继续努力，推动选举改革、要求释放被捕民众、阻止政府骚扰人民。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitpic.com/5nlso7\"><img title=\"A grandma who joined the rally. From the Twitpic page of @eugeneteoh.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/grandma-rally-210x300.jpg\" alt=\"A grandma who joined the rally. From the Twitpic page of @eugeneteoh.\" width=\"210\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>参加游行的老祖母，照片来自Twitpic用户@eugeneteoh</p>\n</div>\n<p>当天在马来西亚的Twitter及Facebook社群里，净选盟游行都是热门话题，民众在網絡上使用各种标签，但<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://search.twitter.com/search?q=&#038;ands=&#038;phrase=&#038;ors=&#038;nots=&#038;tag=bersihstories&#038;lang=en&#038;from=&#038;to=&#038;ref=&#038;near=kuala+lumpur&#038;within=15&#038;units=mi&#038;since=&#038;until=&#038;rpp=20\" href=\"http://search.twitter.com/search?q=&#038;ands=&#038;phrase=&#038;ors=&#038;nots=&#038;tag=bersihstories&#038;lang=en&#038;from=&#038;to=&#038;ref=&#038;near=kuala+lumpur&#038;within=15&#038;units=mi&#038;since=&#038;until=&#038;rpp=20\">##bersihstories</a>似乎最为常见，记录游行现场经验与观察情况。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://trendsmap.com/\"><img title=\"Twitter trending map\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/twitter_bersih-375x163.png\" alt=\"Twitter trending map\" width=\"375\" height=\"163\" /></a></p>\n<p>Twitter趋势地图</p>\n</div>\n<p>以下是人们在Twitter网站上部分反应：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/edryfaizal/status/89715499805589504\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/edryfaizal/status/89715499805589504\">@edryfaizal</a>：许多人说其他民众痛恨我们，但在游行现场，两旁民众和计程车司机向我们挥手，我几乎哭了出来。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/fourfeetnineaud/status/89715832724271104\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/fourfeetnineaud/status/89715832724271104\">@fourfeetnineaud</a>：因为催泪瓦斯，我们几个人被迫躲在Tung Shin医院附近的树丛，还得爬上陡坡。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/elizabethwong/status/89695191484739584\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/elizabethwong/status/89695191484739584\">@elizabethwong</a>：我们走进一家印度烤饼店，向他们要盐巴和茶水，老板非常好心地招呼我们进门坐下。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/lingswaransingh/status/89699176337776640\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/lingswaransingh/status/89699176337776640\">@lingswaransingh</a>：我建议明天每个人都去申诉，指控警方向医院发射催泪瓦斯。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/lilunumlock/status/89701365860933632\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/lilunumlock/status/89701365860933632\">@lilunumlock</a>：这场游行像是马来西亚人民在建立群体精神。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/edmundlaukm/status/89685541775360000\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/edmundlaukm/status/89685541775360000\">@edmundlaukm</a>：看到民众不分种族互助，相当令人兴奋，我们都是同胞，我们都很热情。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2195666297040&#038;set=o.213938935311531&#038;type=1&#038;ref=nf\"><img title=\"Protesters on the run. From the Facebook page of Yuvanesh Prabakaran.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/running-375x206.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters on the run. From the Facebook page of Yuvanesh Prabakaran.\" width=\"375\" height=\"206\" /></a></p>\n<p>逃窜的民众，照片来自Facebook页面Yuvanesh Prabakaran</p>\n</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/jhybe/status/89690802929938433\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/jhybe/status/89690802929938433\">@jhybe</a>：正和其他人盘算如何进入首都，幸好许多人都有带面罩。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/ShazGhaF/status/89685783606345728\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/ShazGhaF/status/89685783606345728\">@ShazGhaF</a>：面对水柱和摧泪瓦斯，还会和你紧靠在一起，这才是真正的朋友。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/mykaernate/status/89681969448890368\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/mykaernate/status/89681969448890368\">@mykaernate</a>：原本我觉得净选盟对国家有害…看过网站后，我明白他们是为了国家团结。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/evelayn/status/89668652592406528\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/evelayn/status/89668652592406528\">@evelayn</a>：我们遭到摧泪瓦斯攻击时，一名男子将手中的盐全部给我们，没有为自己留一些。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/EvangelineHan/status/89675552432197632\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/EvangelineHan/status/89675552432197632\">@EvangelineHan</a>：游行现场掺杂着心碎、胜利与团结气氛，实在很美。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/ninoamigo/status/89673294676099072\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/ninoamigo/status/89673294676099072\">@ninoamigo</a>：我见到男子趴在地上，朝着Merdeka体育馆匍匐前进，不顾雨水和催泪瓦斯。三万人齐声鼓掌。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/lautbulan/status/89667193586974720\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/lautbulan/status/89667193586974720\">@lautbulan</a>：催泪瓦斯攻击时，没有人在意是否狼狈，每个人都在路旁呕吐，这就是团结。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/edryfaizal/status/89674156345528320\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/edryfaizal/status/89674156345528320\">@edryfaizal</a>：行经公寓大楼间的小巷，我以为居民会向我们丢石头，结果他们拍手为我们打气。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10150238394867663&#038;set=o.213938935311531&#038;type=1\"><img title=\"Many were surprised why a hospital was also attacked by the police. From the Facebook page of Fandi Foo.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/hospital-attack-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Many were surprised why a hospital was also attacked by the police. From the Facebook page of Fandi Foo.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>连医院都遭到警方攻击，令许多人震惊，照片来自Facebook页面Fandi Foo</p>\n</div>\n<p>净选盟列出7月9日当天发生事件<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://bersih.org/?p=4352\" href=\"http://bersih.org/?p=4352\">时序表</a>，相关照片请见<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://picasaweb.google.com/104201905154669598873/Bersih2Rally090711?authkey=Gv1sRgCN2Bo8PKqdzNIQ#slideshow/5627215479616199890\" href=\"https://picasaweb.google.com/104201905154669598873/Bersih2Rally090711?authkey=Gv1sRgCN2Bo8PKqdzNIQ#slideshow/5627215479616199890\">Picasaweb</a>和<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo_search.php?oid=213938935311531&#038;view=all\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo_search.php?oid=213938935311531&#038;view=all\">Facebook</a>等网站；Malaysiakini拍摄的影片中，记录一位民众<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZqCmcF7pZZI\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZqCmcF7pZZI\">遭员警殴打</a>。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/09/malaysia-bersih-rally-on-social-media/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/07/13/9535/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E9%A9%AC%E6%9D%A5%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%87%80%E9%80%89%E7%9B%9F%E6%B8%B8%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F07%2F13%2F9535%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F07%2F13%2F9535%2F&#038;desc=%E9%A9%AC%E6%9D%A5%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%87%80%E9%80%89%E7%9B%9F%E6%B8%B8%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span